title: ASTARON Vehicle Sticker Book for Toddlers, Reusable Cute Waterproof Vehicle Stickers, Plane Activities Travel Toys for Kids, Educational Sensory Learning Toy Busy Book
features: 【Learn From Happiness】Puffy Sticker Game Perfect for children practicing fine finger movement, hand-eye coordination, creative expression and other abilities.
【Fun Learning Toys】The jelly stickers in each themed activity book are richly patterned, which helps children understand Transportation.
【Fold-Out Scenes Book】Sticker books can be expanded to larger, rich and interesting play scenarios for children to imagine and create infinite stories.
【Material】Vehicle stickers is made of high quality TPE material,they have adhered well to windows, kitchen island, the refrigerator and pretty much every plastic/glass- like structure.
【Screen-free Play】Sticker games have lots of pretend-play fun. Get kids to reduce their electronic time to protect their eyes and necks
